#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: vk-booking-manager.php
msgid "VK Booking Manager Pro (Beta)"
msgstr "VK Booking Manager Pro (Beta)"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: vk-booking-manager.php
msgid "https://vk-booking-manager.com/"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
#: vk-booking-manager.php
msgid ""
"This is a booking plugin that supports complex service formats such as "
"beauty, chiropractic, and private lessons. It can be used not only on "
"websites but also as a standalone booking system."
msgstr ""
"美容・整体・個人レッスンなど、複雑なサービス形態に対応した予約プラグインで"
"す。ウェブサイト内での使用だけでなく、単体の予約システムとしても運用可能で"
"す。"

#. Author of the plugin
