#: src/admin/class-provider-settings-page.php:1160
msgid ""
"Login by IP is limited to %1$d times/10 minutes, and user registration is "
"limited to %2$d times/30 minutes."
msgstr ""
"IP によるログインは 10 分間に %1$d 回まで、ユーザー登録は 30 分間に %2$d 回ま"
"でに制限されています。"

#: src/admin/class-provider-settings-page.php:1171
msgid "Registration screen redirection"
msgstr "登録画面のリダイレクト"

#: src/admin/class-provider-settings-page.php:1180
